---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Work with John Tang" description="Work with John Tang — naturopath and medical herbalist offering structured, root-cause care for autoimmune and chronic conditions.">
  <Nav />

  <main>
    <section class="practitioner">
      <div class="container">

        <!-- Practitioner header -->
        <div class="practitioner-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">John Tang</div>
            <h1>A structured, integrative approach to chronic and autoimmune conditions</h1>
            <p>Supporting you in navigating complex, long-standing health concerns with a clear, root-cause approach—so you can move forward with greater stability and direction.</p>
            <div class="cta-row">
              <a class="btn primary" href="/booking">Book a consultation</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="qualifications">
              <div class="qual-card">
                <h3>Qualifications</h3>
                <p>BNHM (NZ), BSc (Hons)</p>
              </div>
              <div class="qual-card">
                <h3>Membership</h3>
                <p>NHAA Member</p>
              </div>
              <div class="qual-card">
                <h3>Focus</h3>
                <p>Naturopathy, herbal medicine, autoimmune and chronic health support</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Story blocks -->
        <div class="stack-grid">
          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>A personal beginning</h3>
            <p>My journey into naturopathy and herbal medicine began as an athlete facing an autoimmune condition that conventional medicine couldn't fully resolve.</p>
            <p>For three years, I experimented with diets, supplements, and lifestyle changes, and in the process discovered a deep passion for natural healthcare. It was only after consulting a naturopath and medical herbalist—and experiencing the transformative power of herbs—that I was finally able to step away from pharmaceutical drugs.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>Training and mentorship</h3>
            <p>Inspired by this transformation, I pursued formal training in New Zealand, graduating with a degree in Naturopathy and Herbal Medicine.</p>
            <p>Back in Singapore, I spent five years under the mentorship of a senior naturopath, specialising in Western Herbal Medicine. While the results were encouraging, I felt a disconnect: I was prescribing imported herbs without truly knowing them.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>The birth of Thera Sanctum</h3>
            <p>That realisation led me to establish Thera Sanctum—a sanctuary dedicated to growing, understanding, and integrating local Southeast Asian herbs alongside their Western counterparts.</p>
            <p>Beyond clinical practice, I've rolled up my sleeves to cultivate herbs and hope to conduct workshops soon on natural healthcare and practical herbal medicine. Discovering syntropic agroforestry was another turning point: a regenerative farming model that mirrors God's design and brings holistic healing full circle.</p>
            <p>Today, our work spans consultations and workshops in the city and a developing agroforest in Malacca, where every plant plays a role in healing people and restoring land.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>Looking ahead</h3>
            <p>My vision is to create a holistic retreat where people can experience healing in a natural environment.</p>
            <p>Along the way, I hope to build a community of kindred spirits who cherish nature, share knowledge, and spread a ripple of healing to all who seek it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Band -->
    <section class="cta-band">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>You don't have to keep figuring this out on your own.</h2>
        <p>Book a consultation with John to get a clear, root-cause plan for your condition.</p>
        <div class="cta-row" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/booking">Book a consultation</a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="/contact">Get in touch first</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
